   238	
   239	### 场景 3: Request Timeout — 请求超时 / 模型响应超时
   240	
   241	**症状:**
   242	
   243	Agent 收到以下任一错误:
   244	- HTTP 408 `Request Timeout` / 504 `Gateway Timeout`
   245	- `ReadTimeout` / `ConnectTimeout` / `asyncio.TimeoutError`
   246	- `curl: (28) Operation timed out after ... milliseconds`
   247	- Agent prompt 发送后 >60s 无任何响应
   248	- 流式响应中途停止 >30s (stream interruption)
   249	- `The request timed out. Please try again.`
   250	
   251	**诊断:**
   252	
   253	```bash
   254	# 3-a. 快速延迟探测 (到 API endpoint)
   255	python3 -c "
   256	import json, time, urllib.request, ssl
   257	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   258	for pn, p in c.get('models',{}).get('providers',{}).items():
   259	    url = p.get('baseUrl','')
   260	    if not url: continue
   261	    try:
   262	        ctx = ssl.create_default_context()
   263	        start = time.monotonic()
   264	        req = urllib.request.Request(url + '/models', headers={'User-Agent': 'openclaw-diag/1.0'})
   265	        urllib.request.urlopen(req, timeout=10, context=ctx)
   266	        elapsed = time.monotonic() - start
   267	        print(f'{pn}: connect={elapsed:.2f}s — OK')
   268	    except Exception as e:
   269	        print(f'{pn}: FAILED after {time.monotonic()-start:.2f}s — {type(e).__name__}')
   270	"
   271	
   272	# 3-b. 检查当前超时配置
   273	python3 -c "
   274	import json
   275	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   276	print('requestTimeout:', c.get('requestTimeout', '(default = 60s)'))
   277	print('maxRetries:', c.get('maxRetries', '(default = 3)'))
   278	rt = c.get('requestTimeout')
   279	if rt and rt < 120:
   280	    print('WARNING: timeout < 120s may be too low for large models (Opus, GPT-5)')
   281	"
   282	
   283	# 3-c. 检查系统负载 (排除本地资源争用)
   284	echo "=== System load ==="
   285	uptime
   286	free -h | head -2
   287	
   288	# 3-d. 检查默认 model 是否需要更长的超时
   289	python3 -c "
   290	import json
   291	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   292	model = c.get('agents',{}).get('defaults',{}).get('model','')
   293	LARGE_MODELS = ['claude-opus-4', 'claude-opus-4-8', 'gpt-5', 'gpt-5.5']
   294	if any(m in model for m in LARGE_MODELS):
   295	    print(f'MODEL {model} IS LARGE — recommended timeout >= 120s')
   296	else:
   297	    print(f'model: {model} (standard timeout 60s should suffice)')
   298	"
   299	```
   300	
   301	**诊断决策:**
   302	1. 延迟探测超时 → 网络拥堵或 API 服务降级 → 检查 internet 连接, 检查 provider status page
   303	2. 延迟探测正常但 agent 仍超时 → 超时配置太低 (尤其大模型) → 增大 `requestTimeout`
   304	3. 系统负载高 → 本地资源争用 → 等系统空闲后重试
   305	4. 仅大模型超时 → 大模型冷启动延迟 (>30s) → 增大超时到 120s
   306	
   307	**修复:**
   308	
   309	```bash
   310	# 修复 1: 增大 requestTimeout (推荐默认 60s → 120s)
   311	TS=$(date +%Y%m%d-%H%M%S)
   312	cp ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json ~/.openclaw/openclaw.json.bak.$TS
   313	python3 -c "
   314	import json
   315	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   316	c['requestTimeout'] = 120
   317	json.dump(c, open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json','w'), indent=2)
   318	print('requestTimeout set to 120s')
   319	"
   320	
   321	# 修复 2: 降低 model tier (如果超时持续, 临时切到更小的 model)
   322	# python3 -c "
   323	# import json
   324	# c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   325	# old = c['agents']['defaults']['model']
   326	# c['agents']['defaults']['model'] = 'claude-sonnet-4-6'  # 更快的 fallback
   327	# json.dump(c, open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json','w'), indent=2)
   328	# print(f'Downgraded model: {old} → claude-sonnet-4-6')
   329	# "
   330	
   331	# 修复 3: 检查 provider status page
   332	echo "Check provider status:"
   333	echo "  Anthropic: https://status.anthropic.com"
   334	echo "  OpenAI: https://status.openai.com"
   335	```
   336	
   337	### 场景 4: Model Not Found — 404 / Model 不存在
   338	
   339	**症状:**
   340	
   341	Agent 收到以下任一错误:
   342	- HTTP 404 `Not Found`
   343	- `Model not found: <name>`
   344	- `The model '<name>' does not exist or you do not have access to it`
   345	- Anthropic: `"type":"not_found_error","message":"model: <name>"`
   346	- OpenAI: `"error":{"type":"invalid_request_error","message":"The model '<name>' does not exist"}`
   347	- Claude Code: 启动时提示 `model not found: ...`
   348	
   349	**诊断:**
   350	
   351	```bash
   352	# 4-a. 检查 agent 当前使用的 model name
   353	python3 -c "
   354	import json
   355	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   356	defaults = c.get('agents', {}).get('defaults', {})
   357	print('default_model:', defaults.get('model', '(NOT SET)'))
   358	for an, ac in c.get('agents', {}).items():
   359	    if an == 'defaults': continue
   360	    m = ac.get('model', '')
   361	    if m:
   362	        print(f'agent.{an}.model: {m}')
   363	    else:
   364	        print(f'agent.{an}.model: (inherits default)')
   365	"
   366	
   367	# 4-b. 从 provider API 拉取可用 model 列表 (以 Anthropic 为例)
   368	if [ -n "$ANTHROPIC_API_KEY" ]; then
   369	    echo "=== Available models from api.anthropic.com ==="
   370	    curl -sS --connect-timeout 10 --max-time 30 \
   371	      -H "x-api-key: $ANTHROPIC_API_KEY" \
   372	      -H "anthropic-version: 2023-06-01" \
   373	      https://api.anthropic.com/v1/models \
   374	      | python3 -c "
   375	import json, sys
   376	data = json.load(sys.stdin)
   377	for m in data.get('data', []):
   378	    print(f'  {m[\"id\"]}')" 2>/dev/null || echo "FAILED_TO_FETCH_MODEL_LIST"
   379	fi
   380	
   381	# 4-c. 检查 provider baseUrl 是否正确 (错误的 baseUrl = 错误的 model 命名空间)
   382	python3 -c "
   383	import json
   384	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   385	for pn, p in c.get('models', {}).get('providers', {}).items():
   386	    print(f'{pn}: baseUrl={p.get(\"baseUrl\", \"(default api.anthropic.com)\")!r}')
   387	"
   388	
   389	# 4-d. 常见拼写错误检查
   390	python3 -c "
   391	import json
   392	c = json.load(open('$HOME/.openclaw/openclaw.json'))
   393	model = c.get('agents',{}).get('defaults',{}).get('model','')
   394	KNOWN = {
   395	    'claude-sonnet-4-6': ['claude-sonnet-4.6', 'claude-sonnet-4-5', 'claude-sonnet'],
   396	    'claude-opus-4-8': ['claude-opus-4.8', 'claude-opus-4', 'claude-opus'],
   397	    'claude-haiku-4-5-20251001': ['claude-haiku-4.5', 'claude-haiku-4-5', 'claude-haiku'],
   398	    'claude-fable-5': ['claude-fable', 'fable-5'],
   399	    'gpt-5.5': ['gpt-5-5', 'gpt5.5', 'gpt5'],
   400	    'deepseek-v4-pro': ['deepseek-v4', 'deepseek-v4pro'],
   401	}
   402	model_lower = model.lower().replace('.','-')
   403	for correct, typos in KNOWN.items():
   404	    if model_lower == correct.lower().replace('.','-'):
   405	        print(f'Name looks OK: {model!r} ≈ {correct}')
   406	        break
   407	    for t in typos:
   408	        if model_lower == t.lower().replace('.','-'):
   409	            print(f'LIKELY TYPO: config has {model!r} — did you mean {correct}?')
   410	"
   411	```
   412	
   413	**诊断决策:**
   414	1. Model name 拼写错误 → 修正确切的 model ID → 进入修复 1
   415	2. Model 存在于 provider 但 baseUrl 错误 → provider 配置了错误的 API endpoint → 修正 `baseUrl`
   416	3. Model 在 provider model 列表中不存在 → model 已弃用/改名 → 查 provider docs, 切到后继 model
   417	4. Model 需要单独开通 (Azure, 私有部署) → 部署不存在 → **升级给 operator**
   418	5. API key 正确但 model 列表为空 → 账号没有 model 权限 → **升级给 operator** (需在 provider 控制台开通)
   419	
   420	**修复:**

